description:
&lt;p&gt;Are you a looking for an exciting new opportunity?&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Brooklands Health Centre are looking for a Practice Nurse who will provide care for the presenting patient, treatment, chronic disease management and evaluation of care. Experience in cervical cytology and baby immunisations essential.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;They will work collaboratively with the general practice team to meet the needs of the patients, ensuring that practice policies and procedures are followed.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;They will also assist the Registered Manager with duties related to CQC outcomes, ensuring that compliance is maintained.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;There is staff car parking available onsite and the surgery is served by various bus routes within 2 minute’s walk, it is also only a 5 minute walk from the local shops.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For more information please contact recruitment@operosehealth.co.uk.&lt;/p&gt;
